Conneqt

Models
- Country 
- Region 
- School 
- Association 
- Members 
- Admins 
- Feeds 
- Timetable
- Dues 
- Polls 
- Election 
- Forums 

Country
1. id
2. Name
3. Lat and long
4. createdBy
5. createdAt

Region
1. Id
2. Name
3. Lat and long
4. Country ID
5. createdBy
6. createdAt

School
1. Id
2. Name
3. Location (Country, region, city)
4. createdBy
5. createdAt
6. updatedAt
7. Type (College, High School, Elementary)
8. Gender (male, female, mixed)

Association 
1. Id
2. Name
3. Gender (males, females, mixed)
4. School ID
5. apps (Polls, Timetable, Dues, Forum, Election,Feeds)
6. createdBy
7. createdAt
8. updatedAt

Members (Normal Users And Association Admin)
1. Id
2. Full name 
3. Username (Your index number or fake name)
4. Email
5. Phone
6. Password 
7. Gender (Male, Female)
8. School ID (In UI, choose type to filter schools)
9. createdAt

Member_Association_Permission
1. Id
2. Member ID
3. Association ID
4. permissions: “[“create_poll”,”update_poll”,”delete_poll”,”delete_poll”,etc]”

Admins (Super Admins)
1. Id
2. Name 
3. Email Address
4. Phone Number
5. Password
6. CreatedBy 
7. CreatedAt

Feeds 
1. Id
2. Type (General, Association)
3. Association ID
4. Message 
5. Poll ID
6. createdBy(Could be association admin or super admin)
7. createdAt
8. updatedAt

Feed_Commenting
1. Id
2. Feed ID
3. commentID
4. createdBy
5. Message
6. createdAt

NB: Semester -> to keep track of the semester for each association
Semester
1. Id
2. Academic year
3.  Type (1,2,3)
4. Status (active or deactivate)
5. Association ID
6. createdBy
7. createdAt
8. updatedAt

Dues
1. Id
2. Association ID
3. Semester ID
4. Amount (in pesewas)
5. createdBy
6. createdAt
7. updatedAt


Timetable

TBD


Poll
1. Id
2. Statement
3. Image
4. Status (open, close)
5. createdAt
6. updatedAt

Poll_Single
1. Id
2. Poll Id
3. Type (Image, text)
4. Message
5. Votes
6. createdAt
7. updatedAt

Elections
1. Id
2. Semester ID
3. Association ID
4. Name
5. createdBy
6. createdAt
7. updatedAt

ElectionParticipant
1. Id
2. Election ID
3. Member ID
4. Vetting_Status (passed Or Failed)
5. Votes 
6. createdBy
7. createdAt
8. updatedAt

Forums
1. Id 
2. Type (General, Association)
3. Association ID
4. Name
5. createdBy
6. createdAt
7. updatedAt

Forum_Message
1. Id
2. Message
3. Forum ID
4. createdBy
5. replyingMessage
6. CreatedAt

